io

Class DatabaseEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.DatabaseEntry

  • public class DatabaseEntry
extends java.lang.Object
    Models an "abstract" entry to be written into the database. The database itself may have different tables and this abstract entry can actually be split with its parts being distributed among those tables (while making sure that it is possible to combine the data again).
    Author:
    Ben Kohr
